d 'WXSUM': module to process temperature and precipitation data
d
d      wxsum processes remote sensing rainfall and temperature data
d and outputs useful seasonal statistics. It can    be used with
d either rainfall or temperature data from any source. 
d
d KW: climate
d KW: temperature
d KW: rainfall
d KW: precipitation
d
d Requires: Stata version 
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260613
d
