d Support: email obarriga@@worldbank.org
d
d Author: Aleksandr Michuda,  Swarthmore College 
d Support: email amichud1@@swarthmore.edu
d
d Author: Jeffrey C. Oliver,  University of Arizona 
d Support: email jcoliver@@arizona.edu
d
f wxsum.ado
f wxsum.sthlp
f ../t/temp.dta
f ../r/rain.dta
